{"tid":955033,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"監制係做d乜野？同導演比較邊個影響力大d？","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T12:04:10.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e7080321cb99a99f3e7ad090c07473be285a8e80","tid":955033,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"好多時d名導自己去導演既戲係好得，但到佢去只係去監制既就唔太得，究竟監制係做d乜？"},{"pid":"1f485c6100c19beba828fa8e47855c74281229c9","tid":955033,"uid":10374,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"鳩毛"},{"pid":"3aeb4e14fcb5621ac188688247adddcc7f2f1427","tid":955033,"uid":75610,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1f485c6100c19beba828fa8e47855c74281229c9","tid":955033,"uid":10374,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"鳩毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"Exactly"},{"pid":"982710329d28709f626dd815bfe1f4617e16eef5","tid":955033,"uid":49060,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"以我理解監制一般都係大過導演，主要都係監察住套戲既拍攝進度，有冇拍到走晒樣之類。<br />\n另外就係多數啲名導做監制都係為左提高投資者同觀眾既信心，因為普遍人都對一啲知名度低或者新導演冇咩認識同信心，未必會肯投資或入場，呢個時候一個出名既導演或演員做監制就可以起到作用。<br />\n至於做監制會唔會忍唔住插手干預套戲既拍攝，就一半一半啦。只能講有啲會，有啲唔會。"},{"pid":"d0ba73a0406c977f17b75b895c0cfbf1c85a0707","tid":955033,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"日本有冇監制呢樣嘢？"},{"pid":"83736b6bf4bdd07bb912a6b891ffbe5d0c421889","tid":955033,"uid":170772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"簡單直接 監製掌握錢同關係<br />\n所以行政上 地位係高過導演<br />\n創作上就視乎兩者係行內既地位"},{"pid":"33ac19bffe2d546cc4d04e7b8f3258352df86a4c","tid":955033,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"電影: 導演大<br />\n電視: 監製大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\